data.description: Seller will accept or counter offers between $349,900 and $359,900. Your new home has it all, location, privacy, style, and quality.  You love being so close to two major shopping centers, but not having to deal with traffic and road noise.  You enjoy your picturesque neighborhood nestled next to a massive orchard.  Your privacy is unmatched with no rear neighbor and location on a cul-de-sac.  Most of all you love the sense of elegance and style that permeates through your entire residence.  It screams luxury.  From your walk-in full body massage tub, to your chic Iceland grey granite countertops, new designer carpet, and modernized olive cabinetry everything is tailormade for your lifestyle.  As if that was not enough you also benefit from one of the lowest utility costs around.  All Energy Star rated appliances, heating, cooling, lighting, plumbing, windows, OWNED SOLAR, and spray foam in the walls and attic make your utility bills a laugh.  Electric bill what's that?  At the top of the range the seller will also install a generator to ensure you never have to touch the grid for power.  It's too good to be true, but pinch yourself it's real.  Now, when do you want your keys?
